# Current Task Handoff

## Latest User Instruction

Summarize the newest user request here.

## Goal

State the concrete outcome the next worker should preserve or finish.

## Non-Goals

List adjacent work that should not be done.

## Files/Areas Owned

List files or subsystems touched by this task.

## Recent Actions

Short chronological bullets of what was changed or verified.

## Decisions Made

Record decisions that matter for continuation. Durable architecture decisions
belong in `docs/decisions/`.

## Verification Evidence

List commands run and outcomes, or explain why verification has not run yet.

## Handoff Status

Use one: `continue`, `blocked`, or `complete`.

## Remaining Risks

List known risks, uncertainties, or follow-up checks.
